light and dark have fought ceaselessly

5
00:03:43,000 --> 00:03:46,450
for dominion over the world.

6
00:03:45,000 --> 00:03:48,000
The Broken Promise

7
00:03:47,350 --> 00:03:50,000
Whispers echo of a dark lord whose insidious

8
00:03:50,000 --> 00:03:52,550
grip on the realm is marked by insatiable...

9
00:03:52,550 --> 00:03:53,950
...lust.

10
00:03:55,750 --> 00:03:57,250
Twisted jealousy,

11
00:03:57,250 --> 00:03:59,250
ravenous greed,

12
00:03:59,250 --> 00:04:02,150
unrelenting vanity,

13
00:04:02,150 --> 00:04:06,050
and possessive manipulation.

14
00:04:06,750 --> 00:04:10,550
A group of adventurers rose to face this threat,

15
00:04:10,550 --> 00:04:15,950
with hidden wishes of secrets and shadows untold.

16
00:04:16,850 --> 00:04:18,850
First, there was Nameless,

17
00:04:18,850 --> 00:04:21,850
quick as an owl in the night.

18
00:04:21,000 --> 00:04:24,000
WANTED: STOLEN STRAWBERRY CAKE

19
00:04:21,850 --> 00:04:27,550
A thrill-seeking thief she was, who hunted in the fringes of society.

20
00:04:28,950 --> 00:04:34,250
Next was Cora, a passionate chronomancer and hostess,

21
00:04:34,250 --> 00:04:37,000
whose connections to this world felt as thin as

22
00:04:37,000 --> 00:04:39,000
the threads of time she manipulated

23
00:04:39,000 --> 00:04:40,850
to build her harem.

24
00:04:42,550 --> 00:04:46,350
Faelin was a guardian of nature

25
00:04:46,350 --> 00:04:49,000
whose sweet, charming exterior

26
00:04:49,000 --> 00:04:53,750
belied her true nature.

27
00:04:54,650 --> 00:04:58,250
Descended from the heavens, Irisa brought...

28
00:05:00,008 --> 00:05:02,108
...tidings of doom.

29
00:05:02,108 --> 00:05:05,108
Her innocent and clumsy demeanor...

30
00:05:05,108 --> 00:05:10,508
...stood in contrast to her perfectionist tendencies.

31
00:05:12,308 --> 00:05:13,708
Lastly,

32
00:05:13,708 --> 00:05:18,408
Hexa, a bard who had yet to find her spotlight.

33
00:05:18,408 --> 00:05:21,808
Dazzling were her performances,

34
00:05:21,808 --> 00:05:27,508
whilst her silent dreams of recognition gnawed at her heart.

35
00:05:28,908 --> 00:05:33,208
On a warm summer night, amidst the flickering candlelight...

36
00:05:33,208 --> 00:05:35,808
...of the Singing Shark Inn,

37
00:05:35,808 --> 00:05:40,408
they found their fates intertwined with that of...

38
00:05:40,408 --> 00:05:43,108
...a malevolent Dark Lord,

39
00:05:43,108 --> 00:05:47,408
whose shadow slowly consumed everything in their path.

40
00:05:59,708 --> 00:06:01,408
Hey Faelyn.

41
00:06:01,408 --> 00:06:03,808
How dost thou cope with death?

42
00:06:03,808 --> 00:06:05,708
The fear thereof, I mean.

43
00:06:07,108 --> 00:06:10,308
Hmm, tending to my plants does help...

44
00:06:10,308 --> 00:06:13,108
...stave off the looming spectre of the void, if but for a spell.

45
00:06:14,208 --> 00:06:15,508
Plants, huh?

46
00:06:15,508 --> 00:06:16,708
Tried that once.

47
00:06:16,708 --> 00:06:18,008
Killed them all.

48
00:06:18,008 --> 00:06:21,008
Guess I'm destined to bring death one way or another.

49
00:06:21,708 --> 00:06:25,508
Perhaps thou art stick to nursing pints rather than plants, Hexa.

50
00:06:25,808 --> 00:06:28,108
Nature's children are precious.

51
00:06:28,108 --> 00:06:30,108
Thy liver is not.

52
00:06:31,408 --> 00:06:33,608
Haha! I'll drink to that!

53
00:06:36,708 --> 00:06:38,208
Comely maiden,

54
00:06:38,208 --> 00:06:40,208
might I follow thee home?

55
00:06:40,208 --> 00:06:43,608
'Twas my mother's wish that I follow my dreams.

56
00:06:44,208 --> 00:06:46,408
A fine distraction, Kora.

57
00:06:47,308 --> 00:06:50,008
Namu is so clever, isn't she?

58
00:06:50,508 --> 00:06:54,008
Thou mistakest me for thine accomplice, Namu.

59
00:06:54,008 --> 00:06:58,508
Canst thou not see I am trying to work my magic here?

60
00:06:59,108 --> 00:07:02,508
Already resorting to time magic to ensnare thy quarry?

61
00:07:03,008 --> 00:07:05,108
'Twas but a turn of phrase.

62
00:07:05,108 --> 00:07:07,708
I hardly need magic to court a maiden fair.

63
00:07:07,708 --> 00:07:10,108
Merely my unending charm.

64
00:07:10,508 --> 00:07:12,708
Hast thou not enough trinkets already?

65
00:07:13,108 --> 00:07:15,108
I take no more than I need to survive.

66
00:07:15,108 --> 00:07:16,308
I promise.

67
00:07:16,808 --> 00:07:17,608
Woohoo!

68
00:07:17,608 --> 00:07:21,008
It would seem at least someone is getting lucky tonight!

69
00:07:21,008 --> 00:07:22,408
Let me see.

70
00:07:22,408 --> 00:07:23,708
What'd you get?

71
00:07:28,708 --> 00:07:29,408
Fie!

72
00:07:29,408 --> 00:07:30,508
Here comes the guard!

73
00:07:30,508 --> 00:07:32,408
That is my cue to vanish.

74
00:07:32,408 --> 00:07:33,508
Namu,

75
00:07:33,508 --> 00:07:38,208
methinks the guard doth not arrive bathed in heavenly light.

76
00:07:39,108 --> 00:07:41,208
Greetings, esteemed patrons!

77
00:07:41,208 --> 00:07:44,208
I seek stouthearted souls to accompany me...

78
00:07:44,208 --> 00:07:46,008
...on a dangerous—

79
00:07:46,208 --> 00:07:47,308
Aah!

80
00:07:48,808 --> 00:07:51,108
How charming.

81
00:07:53,708 --> 00:07:56,808
‘Tis not a journey to be taken lightly.

82
00:07:56,808 --> 00:08:00,008
The darkness grows stronger by the day.

83
00:08:00,008 --> 00:08:04,208
Join me, and thy deepest wish will be granted.

84
00:08:04,208 --> 00:08:05,508
Deepest wish?

85
00:08:05,908 --> 00:08:08,008
Sounds like a ruse to me.

86
00:08:08,008 --> 00:08:09,108
What think you?

87
00:08:09,608 --> 00:08:10,808
Might be,

88
00:08:10,808 --> 00:08:12,708
but what if it's not?

89
00:08:13,608 --> 00:08:15,508
Oi, shiny lady!

90
00:08:15,508 --> 00:08:17,008
We're all ears.

91
00:08:17,008 --> 00:08:19,408
So go on, spin us your tale.

92
00:08:19,808 --> 00:08:21,508
How can we trust thee?

93
00:08:21,508 --> 00:08:23,508
Who art thou, anyway?

94
00:08:24,008 --> 00:08:26,508
I understand your skepticism.

95
00:08:26,508 --> 00:08:29,508
In times like these, we all have our doubts.

96
00:08:29,808 --> 00:08:31,208
My name is IRyssa.

97
00:08:31,208 --> 00:08:34,508
I descended from the celestial realm on a holy quest...

98
00:08:34,508 --> 00:08:36,708
...to end the Dark Lord's reign.

99
00:08:37,008 --> 00:08:40,808
‘Tis foretold that by vanquishing the Dark Lord,

100
00:08:40,808 --> 00:08:43,108
