101
00:08:43,708 --> 00:08:46,808
What dost thou mean by our heart's desire?

102
00:08:47,408 --> 00:08:51,308
Each of you carries within you a longing that drives you.

103
00:08:51,308 --> 00:08:55,208
This quest can make those aspirations a reality.

104
00:08:55,308 --> 00:08:57,108
Have you any proof?

105
00:09:05,108 --> 00:09:06,108
There.

106
00:09:06,108 --> 00:09:08,908
Now dost thou believe me?

107
00:09:09,608 --> 00:09:11,208
Kora, what is wrong?

108
00:09:11,208 --> 00:09:14,308
Thou lookest as though thou hast seen a ghost.

109
00:09:14,408 --> 00:09:18,008
What witchcraft hast thou wrought upon her, foul enchantress?

110
00:09:18,508 --> 00:09:21,308
I only showed her the truth.

111
00:09:22,308 --> 00:09:23,708
