188
00:16:00,524 --> 00:16:01,624
What was that?!

189
00:16:01,824 --> 00:16:04,524
They looked around but saw nothing.

190
00:16:04,524 --> 00:16:08,024
Spooked by the unnatural sound, they decided to leave.

191
00:16:08,024 --> 00:16:11,524
But 'twas too late. They'd lost track of time.

192
00:16:11,524 --> 00:16:15,024
Night had fallen, and darkness shrouded the woods.

193
00:16:15,024 --> 00:16:18,524
They split up and marked their path with berries.

194
00:16:18,524 --> 00:16:21,524
After some time, Gumi heard a scream

195
00:16:21,524 --> 00:16:23,824
followed by a bone-chilling crunch.

196
00:16:23,824 --> 00:16:28,024
Gumi ran down the berry trail with all the haste she could muster.

197
00:16:28,024 --> 00:16:32,024
The berries underfoot began to ooze a strange red substance.

198
00:16:32,024 --> 00:16:36,024
It seeped into the ground, each stain bigger than the last.

199
00:16:36,024 --> 00:16:40,024
Breathless, she came upon a large puddle of red.

200
00:16:40,024 --> 00:16:43,024
And in the center, a pile of teeth.

201
00:16:43,024 --> 00:16:48,024
Frozen in horror, she looked up and beheld a grotesque hag looming over her,

202
00:16:48,024 --> 00:16:51,524
Darla's hair hanging from her mouth.

203
00:16:51,524 --> 00:16:55,024
Before she could react, the hag lunged!

204
00:16:55,524 --> 00:17:00,024
How mean to rob us of any chance of peaceful slumber.

205
00:17:00,024 --> 00:17:03,024
Merely trying to keep you all on your toes.

206
00:17:03,024 --> 00:17:07,024
It's working. I don't think I'll sleep a wink tonight.

207
00:17:07,824 --> 00:17:11,024
Let us abscond from this place.

208
00:17:11,024 --> 00:17:13,524
Starting to feel like we're being watched.

209
00:17:14,024 --> 00:17:15,524
Oh, wise choice.

210
00:17:16,024 --> 00:17:18,024
None of you belong here.

